### Get a pool
GET {{baseUrl}}/pools/01H1CFJB0Y3KK357WCA2HB5MCX HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{authToken}}


### Get the pool scores of a pool
GET {{baseUrl}}/pools/01K2ZFAMNSXRBHWXABZQ5WWA7K/gamblers HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{authToken}}


### Get the pools of a gambler
GET {{baseUrl}}/gamblers/01K2WBEKVNGG7A5BZPM14QFFFS/pools HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{authToken}}


### Get the pool score by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/pools/01H1CFJB0Y3KK357WCA2HB5MCX/gamblers/01H1CMCDHH99FH8FDY36S0YH3A HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{authToken}}


### Get pendings bet
GET {{baseUrl}}/pools/01KNEXN00B70FQJW81FJQ5B0TX/gamblers/01K2WBEKVNGG7A5BZPM14QFFFS/bets/pending HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{authToken}}


### Get finished bet
GET {{baseUrl}}/pools/01H1CFJB0Y3KK357WCA2HB5MCX/gamblers/01H1CMCDHH99FH8FDY36S0YH3A/bets/finished HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{authToken}}


